Package edu.rit.slides.test

Package edu.rit.slides.test contains test programs for the Slides application in package edu.rit.slides.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
SlideShow01 Class SlideShow01 is a main program that creates a certain SlideShow and stores it in a file.
SlideShow02 Class SlideShow02 is a main program that creates a certain SlideShow and stores it in a file.
Test01 Class Test01 is a main program that creates a simple SlideShow and stores it in a file.
 

Package edu.rit.slides.test Description

Package edu.rit.slides.test contains test programs for the Slides application in package edu.rit.slides. The slide show files "SlideShow01.ss", "SlideShow02.ss", and "Test01.ss" were created by the main programs SlideShow01, SlideShow02, and Test01, respectively.
